{"tid":1837690,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【帶風向】與其派利是比保安，不如派比大廈清潔工","createTime":"2020-01-23T17:33:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-06T06:18:39.000Z","uid":76508,"like":52,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"0d8da1f7170e83c0cb7afff9320c00c5f9653899","tid":1837690,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:33:29.000Z","msg":"特登夜晚開po，以免影響行動po<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">盡忠職守既保安照派</span><br />\n<br />\n&bull;  清潔一向係低層職業，外判公司，人工福利都唔高<br />\n我覺得佢地先係真正撐起社會，如果唔係低學歷，試諗下佢地搞罷工會點？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&bull;  年近歲晚，垃圾多到仆街，偏偏一直以黎香港人都係冇乜公德心。希望各位垃圾好好放入膠袋、包好、再放入垃圾桶，有時見到啲飯汁周圍滴，真係諗起都辛苦<br />\n<br />\n&bull;  而家風頭火勢，你班人除完啲口罩周圍dum，又唔用膠袋包好，搞到佢地打份工極高風險，係正常人既<span style=\"color: red;\">幾十倍</span>，封返啲利是比佢地都好應該啦！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n明明有啲職業做實事又冇人理，有啲職業無所事事就年年收利是收到手軟。"},{"pid":"893274dff1c0f9dbb7665fe941c36c47ef833ee5","tid":1837690,"uid":76508,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:34:36.000Z","msg":"希望有人認同，唔好再益啲無所事事既保安"},{"pid":"05999be3104abf9977b90c5eb32937df087cb7d5","tid":1837690,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:36:26.000Z","msg":"推 1/10"},{"pid":"318544d913d0feae27f276c358413bc6e8642963","tid":1837690,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:36:40.000Z","msg":"推 2/10"},{"pid":"8dacfdcb47f7322b28677f22621e710ff1570bab","tid":1837690,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:36:52.000Z","msg":"推 3/10"},{"pid":"832eb482e102f45759e9b9f0f13d68f798b72c76","tid":1837690,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:37:04.000Z","msg":"推4/10"},{"pid":"f4274832b0c247856b733d6731ab6583e9a8abae","tid":1837690,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-23T17:37:30.000Z","msg":"推 5/10"},{"pid":"7351200c92ed3a4fceedac4621466531ad45974a","tid":1837690,"uid":76508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTi